ArcGIS,REST,API,Location,Allocation,service,assists,users,to,choose,locations,from,a,list,of,facilities,based,on,probable,interactions,The,site,offers,required,parameters,that,include,demand,points,tokens,and,facilities,The,website,also,shows,optional,parameters,that,include,analysis,region,target,market,share,and,travel,mode,Users,can,access,a,data,coverage,page,and,code,examples,with,JSON,responses,for,various,requests